comments: Butler (MIA) is moving alongside James' (LAL) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
James (LAL) initiates contact with Lowry (MIA), who has established a legal guarding position in his path.
James (LAL) legally contests Butler's (MIA) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
James (LAL) cleanly blocks Lowry's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
James (LAL) is firming up over his left foot in Herro's (MIA) path and the contact during the pick is marginal.
Reaves (LAL) establishes his right foot as his pivot foot, and he keeps his pivot foot planted to the floor during his shot fake.
Reddish (LAL) steps slightly forward towards Butler (MIA) and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Wood (LAL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Reaves (LAL) slides his hand across Adebayo's (MIA) front and the contact during the pick is marginal.
Reaves (LAL) brings his hands toward Butler (MIA) and marginal contact occurs as Reaves releases away from the pick.
Reddish (LAL) brushes Lowry's (MIA) arm and marginal contact occurs as Lowry completes his desired pass.
Reddish (LAL) is moving alongside Butler's (MIA) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive.
Adebayo (MIA) lifts and re-plants his pivot foot prior to releasing his dribble.
Adebayo (MIA) and Wood (LAL) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Reaves (LAL) establishes himself in Butler's (MIA) path and he absorbs the contact to his upper body.
Butler (MIA) brings his forearm towards James' (LAL) front and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Highsmith (MIA) legally contests Reddish's (LAL) jump shot attempt.
Richardson (MIA) and Reaves (LAL) come together in pursuit of the rebound and marginal contact occurs as they attempt to secure the loose ball.
